  "notes": "Central Galician (Lugo, eastern A Coruña, Ourense). Closest to RAG standard norms. No gheada (no /ɣ/ for /g/), no seseo, no yeísmo. 7-vowel system with /ɛ, ɔ/ as phonemes. Palatal lateral /ʎ/ fully preserved. Standard lenition: /ɡ/ → [ɣ] in intervocalic position. This is the prestige norm base used for the RAG standard.",
